#1564. <strong>Adam Alter</strong> is a Professor of Marketing at New York University’s Stern School of Business and the author of two books, Drunk Tank Pink, and Irresistible: The Rise of Addictive Technology and the Business of Keeping Us Hooked.<p><img src="http://podcasts.joerogan.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/JRE1564.jpg" width="580" alt="" /></p>